supermon-ng (4.2.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Full Apache support: modules, site file, default site disable, reload.
  * Add scripts/configure-apache.sh (shared with install.sh).
  * debconf prompts for Apache setup, default sites, and site refresh on upgrade.
  * postinst enables/starts systemd units; prerm/postrm manage Apache site lifecycle.

